snippet.title: Pokémon first discovered in the Paldea region are coming to Pokémon GO!
snippet.description:
Trainers,

Get ready to encounter even more Pokémon on your journey!

Pokémon originally discovered in the Paldea region of the Pokémon Scarlet and Pokémon Violet games for Nintendo Switch are coming to Pokémon GO starting this September.

Stay tuned for more details!"
